{"tid":1303140,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一子錯，每盤皆落索，睇嚟我占奔都係時候離開了","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:16.000Z","uid":154872,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd2489326af74ba5fb173f859027fd6ad7f1cb0","tid":1303140,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"Every step that i take is another mistake to you<br />\n<br />\n冇面目留低了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSayonara<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期on9事件回顧<br />\n<br />\n1. 原來唔小心啟蒙咗CC台班撚屌fake鳩同路手足們出海富<br />\n<br />\n警員咁喜歡上來連登搵料同搭人，我地扮有義士資料/行動資訊整大量Fake link撚鳩佢地<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284869</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 迷Angela<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌奶星Ａｎｇｅｌａ前男友原來係阿蛇仲Ｔｉｎｄｅｒ周圍約扑野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dgLKtS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dgLKtS</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 去金拱門食１８件勿樂基<br />\n<br />\n開咗嗰兩隻咩咸蛋黃同南乳燒味醬嚟點<br />\n<br />\n食到我即刻回想起一生中做過嘅所有錯事<br />\n<br />\n難食到食完要懺悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635eb1921633115ef39c0d565b4d8ebcab2fc581","tid":1303140,"uid":10402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"挽留"},{"pid":"dc4ea6fe2ff5abfc0c0e0284d40e1068ae5f1fd5","tid":1303140,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"不要走"},{"pid":"55a1bd493b5695aac53c1d4e60e1bbd7be70f